# External plugin packages (the AI coach) are published to GitHub Packages under
# the @theangryraven scope. Installing them needs a GitHub token with
# read:packages, exposed to the build as NODE_AUTH_TOKEN (set as a build secret
# in Lovable). The scope line below only affects @theangryraven/* — if no such
# package is depended on, an unset token is harmless and npm never hits this
# registry. See src/plugins/README.md.
@theangryraven:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
